Code to combine the high precision measurements of satellite properties with a cosmological simulation to estimate the mass of its host galaxy's halo.


Authors: 
- Ekta Patel (University of Arizona)
- Gurtina Besla (University of Arizona)
- Kaisey Mandel (Harvard University)


Dependencies:
- numpy
- matplotlib
- scipy
- IPython
- Illustris simulation (optional; see http://www.illustris-project.org/)
